### Variables
@baseUrl = https://apiv2.pomodify.site/api/v2
@accessToken = paste_access_token_here
@token = paste_fcm_token_here

### Register push token (JWT required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/push/register-token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### Unregister push token (JWT required)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/push/unregister-token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get push status (registered + enabled)
GET {{baseUrl}}/push/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Disable push notifications (keep token stored)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/push/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Enable push notifications
PUT {{baseUrl}}/push/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
